\par \tab }{\b\fs24 Duties of the Priest:}{\fs24  Guidance, Marriage. Judgement: Priests of this god are asked to be judges at all athletic events, to help ensure fairness in the sport. (A given event won't necessarily have }{\i\fs24 only }{\fs24 
