y these priests.) Vigilance: Against unfairness. Priests of this god loathe unfairness and dishonesty above all other human traits. This isn't just unfairness in the sports arena: They also oppose unjust rule. Additionally, when two forces of basically eq
ual honor and righteousness clash, these priests, if they choose to become involved, tend to support the weaker side, the underdog.
