\par \tab }{\b\fs24 Spheres of Influence:}{\fs24  Major Access to All, Divination, Necromantic. Minor Access to Elemental, Guardian.
\par \tab }{\b\fs24 Powers:}{\fs24  The priest, even at first level, can cast the }{\i\fs24 detect lies}{\fs24  spell three times per day in addition to all other spells. }{\i\fs24 At 3rd Level:}{\fs24  }{\i\fs24 Inspire Fear}{\fs24 
 (as per the Designing Faiths chapter).
