\par }{\b\fs22\cf2 Marriage}{\fs24 
\par \tab  
\par \tab This god is a deity of the bond of matrimony. Whether marriage is considered to be a holy alliance or merely an im
portant contract, this god represents marriage in all its aspects: Affection, love, jealousy, argument, home, children, development, and compromise.
\par \tab The priesthood of this god promotes marriage as a way of life. They approve of lovers, but not lovers }{\i\fs24 staying}{\fs24 
 lovers without ever being wed. They act as "marriage counselors" for any couple who asks their help in working out marital problems.
\par \tab The god of marriage is as likely to be male as female.
\par \tab The priests of this god are on good terms with the priests of Birth/Children, Community, Culture, Love, and Race.
\par \tab }{\b\fs24 Alignment:}{\fs24  The deity is neutral good. The priests may be any sort of good alignment. The flock may be of any neutral or good alignment.
