onweapon proficiency slot which may only be used for languages); the language chosen must be of a sentient humanoid race. }{\i\fs24 Soothing Word}{\fs24  (as per the Designing Faiths chapter). At 8th level:}{\i\fs24  Charm/Fascination}{\fs24 
 (as per the Designing Faiths chapter).
