 ability: Success on roll of 1 on 1d6 when passing within 10', 1-2 on 1d6 to find secret doors and 1-3 on 1d6 to find concealed portals when actively searching; elven priests of this order have success on a roll of 1-2 when passing within 10', 1-3 to find
 secret doors and 1-4 to find concealed portals when actively searching).}{\i\fs24  Infravision}{\fs24  (same as the elf ability; an elven or half-elven priest of this faith has Infravision of doubled range, to 120'). }{\i\fs24 Turn Undead}{\fs24 
