\par }{\b\fs22\cf2 Time}{\fs24 
\par \tab  
\par \tab This god is the deity of the march of time. He represents inevitability -- not destiny based on the will of individual gods, but the inevitability of change brought on by time.
\par \tab His priests preach the philosophy of patience to the flock, and help all the members of the flock adapt themselves to their changing bodies, lifestyles, and needs as they go through life.
\par \tab The time-god is male.
